high_descs: Turn around, walk across the room to the fridge, turn left, take a few steps and turn right to face the coffee maker
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee maker
Turn right and go to the sink
Put the mug into the sink, wash it, and pick it up
Go back to the coffee maker
Place the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a washed mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: pick up white mug from coffee maker
wash and remove mug from sink
put white mug inside coffee maker
anns.task_desc: put washed mug inside coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge then turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the dirty mug that's in front of you at the coffee maker..
Turn around and walk to the sink then turn left to face it.
Wash the mug in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and walk back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug back where you got it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug at the coffee maker.
